edu.ncsu.csc216.shipping_simulator.pkg

Class RegularBookShipment

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc216.shipping_simulator.pkg.ItemToShip
      • edu.ncsu.csc216.shipping_simulator.pkg.RegularBookShipment

  • public class RegularBookShipment
extends ItemToShip
    RegularBookShipment is a child of ItemToShip. It represents a regular book shipment in the simulation. Regular shipments can go in regular and international shipment process stations. These shipments are also colored blue
    Author:
    Aurora Bravo
